1
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,320
Inspector

2
00:01:11,040 --> 00:01:11,800
You're finally back.

3
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:14,440
What's wrong?

4
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:15,880
These are a few telegrams

5
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:17,120
Adjutant Du just received.

6
00:01:17,520 --> 00:01:18,120
I took a look.

7
00:01:18,600 --> 00:01:19,440
They are all from the generals,

8
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:20,200
asking about

9
00:01:20,720 --> 00:01:21,480
the Marshal's funeral

10
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,360
and when it will be held.

11
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,840
Reply to the uncles.

12
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:29,200
Tell them my father's funeral

13
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,080
will be held at the Marshal's mansion in three days.

14
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:32,200
Please ask them to be there

15
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:33,720
to see my father off one last time.

16
00:01:34,360 --> 00:01:34,880
Yes.

17
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:38,840
Inspector,

18
00:01:39,240 --> 00:01:40,160
regarding the Marshal's case,

19
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,680
we don't have a single clue right now.

20
00:01:42,240 --> 00:01:43,040
If those generals

21
00:01:43,040 --> 00:01:43,600
come

22
00:01:43,840 --> 00:01:44,840
and ask about the killer,

23
00:01:45,720 --> 00:01:46,440
what will you say?

24
00:01:47,720 --> 00:01:48,360
Yeah.

25
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:49,960
Making such arrangements,

26
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,320
do you have a plan?

27
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:52,560
You all know

28
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:53,920
I've always suspected the killer

29
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,320
is someone close to my parents.

30
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,320
But recently,

31
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,320
I've asked all the elders in the family,

32
00:01:58,960 --> 00:02:00,040
and none of them know anything.

33
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:04,480
Inspector,

34
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,160
take your time.

35
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:06,040
Don't rush.

36
00:02:12,640 --> 00:02:13,560
Those uncles

37
00:02:13,920 --> 00:02:14,640
and my father

38
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,200
had more or less

39
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,040
some interactions when he was alive.

40
00:02:17,840 --> 00:02:18,840
Perhaps they know some things

41
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:19,760
that we don't.

42
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,000
Maybe

43
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,760
we can find

44
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,000
some clues from them.

45
00:02:26,200 --> 00:02:27,560
But the situation is complicated now.

46
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,640
After they arrive,

47
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,120
what if...

48
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,720
I know what you're worried about.

49
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,760
With my father dead,

50
00:02:33,200 --> 00:02:34,000
Jiangyu City's

51
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,360
military and political power is vacant.

52
00:02:35,640 --> 00:02:37,400
All the warlords are eyeing it covetously,

53
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:38,920
eager to take a piece of the pie immediately.

54
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,920
But to find out the truth,

55
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:43,120
I have to do this.

56
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,200
Chun Cheng,

57
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:46,400
make arrangements for me.

58
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,200
Have them strengthen

59
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,280
the security of the Marshal's mansion

60
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,760
to ensure nothing goes wrong

61
00:02:51,120 --> 00:02:51,840
during the funeral.

62
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,280
Yes.

63
00:03:00,640 --> 00:03:01,200
How are you?

64
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:05,840
I'm fine.

65
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:00,840
General Ling

66
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,000
and General Qi have arrived!

67
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:03,520
Young Master,

68
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:04,840
General Ling

69
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:05,680
and General Qi

70
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:05,960
have arrived.

71
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,000
Brother!

72
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,320
Brother!

73
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,840
Brother!

74
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,120
Brother!

75
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,960
You left us too soon!

76
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:15,080
Brother!

77
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,560
Old Ling and I

78
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:17,800
have come to see you.

79
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:19,960
Brother!

80
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:21,840
Rest in peace.

81
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,960
Worthy nephew,

82
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:42,120
with the Marshal gone,

83
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:43,280
Jiangyu City

84
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,800
seems to have lost its backbone.

85
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,720
Even though you are his son,

86
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:47,720
but

87
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:49,520
this military and political power

88
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,520
is not so easy to take over.

89
00:04:52,320 --> 00:04:53,000
Jinrong,

90
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:54,080
it's not that I

91
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,720
underestimate you.

92
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,000
These military and political affairs

93
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,160
are very complicated.

94
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:58,680
How old are you anyway?

95
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,080
You've never experienced such things.

96
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,080
Besides,

97
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:03,120
the Marshal

98
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,800
worked hard to build this empire.

99
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,840
It can't just be ruined like this.

100
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:08,160
General Ling,

101
00:05:08,960 --> 00:05:09,560
General Qi,

102
00:05:10,240 --> 00:05:11,840
I respect you two as my father's sworn brothers.

103
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:14,120
But bringing this up at his funeral,

104
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,520
isn't it a bit too abrupt?

105
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,520
Moreover, these military and political affairs

106
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:19,560
are not for you to decide.

107
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:20,760
They are for me to decide.

108
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,640
The stability of Jiangyu City

109
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,760
was fought for by us old folks

110
00:05:28,400 --> 00:05:29,520
with our lives.

111
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:32,200
You're just a wet-behind-the-ears kid.

112
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:33,440
How could you understand

113
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,640
the intricacies of it?

114
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:36,320
You...

115
00:05:38,320 --> 00:05:39,760
Thank you for your concern, Uncles.

116
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:41,200
This military and political power

117
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:42,520
is the Huang Family's internal affair.

118
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,520
I can still handle it for now.

119
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,840
If there is a need in the future,

120
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,280
I will ask you two Uncles

121
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,200
for your help.

122
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:52,960
However, there is one thing

123
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,440
I would like to ask

124
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:55,320
you two Uncles about.

125
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:57,440
What is it?

126
00:05:57,840 --> 00:05:58,640
You two Uncles

127
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,720
have known my parents for years.

128
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:01,200
Do you know

129
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:02,440
if my parents, when alive,

130
00:06:03,760 --> 00:06:04,760
knew anyone

131
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:05,560
that I don't know?

132
00:06:09,640 --> 00:06:10,440
You asking this,

133
00:06:10,960 --> 00:06:11,880
could it be you suspect

134
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,200
your father's death

135
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,960
is related to this

136
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:15,960
so-called friend?

137
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,520
No.

138
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:18,000
I just think

139
00:06:18,280 --> 00:06:18,640
if there really is

140
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:19,520
such a person,

141
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,000
as a junior,

142
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,440
I should pass the news of my father's death

143
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,560
on to him,

144
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:24,960
just to show my respect.

145
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:30,080
Your father and we

146
00:06:30,320 --> 00:06:31,320
all came from the same military academy

147
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,640
as sworn brothers.

148
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,120
But now,

149
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:37,440
only us old folks are left.

150
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,200
Since you want to show respect,

151
00:06:40,960 --> 00:06:42,200
you'd better think carefully

152
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,320
about our proposal just now.

153
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:53,520
General Ling,

154
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,400
General Qi,

155
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:55,400
the reception room

156
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:56,720
has refreshments prepared for everyone.

157
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:57,840
Please head over there.

158
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:01,120
No need.

159
00:07:01,760 --> 00:07:02,840
We won't be eating.

160
00:07:11,520 --> 00:07:12,840
Don't get mad at them.

161
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,520
They're just here to cause trouble.

162
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,320
The most urgent task now

163
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,400
is to stabilize the situation first

164
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:18,760
and find the killer.

165
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,640
Fellow townsfolk,

166
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,280
the disasters of the Huang Family

167
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,000
are a warning from heaven.

168
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,000
The peace of Jiangyu City

169
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:02,080
has been destroyed by their sins.

170
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,960
Only my Safety Amulet

171
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:05,320
can protect you all

172
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,640
from being implicated.

173
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:08,880
I want one!

174
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,200
Please calm down, everyone.

175
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,120
One at a time.

176
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,880
The Sorceress will keep you safe.

177
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:13,880
Please, everyone.

178
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,440
Thank you, Sorceress.

179
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:29,760
Sister,

180
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:30,960
why did you put so much

181
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:31,640
money in there?

182
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,640
You don't know,

183
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:33,520
this Sorceress

184
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,640
is truly a living immortal.

185
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,760
Come, folks, this way please.

186
00:08:35,880 --> 00:08:36,720
My daughter was seriously ill.

187
00:08:36,880 --> 00:08:37,960
Yesterday, I was right here

188
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,080
and asked for a Safety Amulet.

189
00:08:39,560 --> 00:08:40,440
I went back and put it on her.

190
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:41,640
And guess

191
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,200
what happened?

192
00:08:42,640 --> 00:08:43,080
What?

193
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,320
My daughter's illness

194
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,200
was miraculously cured!

195
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,000
Really?

196
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:49,120
Really? That's amazing!

197
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,200
It's absolutely true.

198
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,280
That's why

199
00:08:51,560 --> 00:08:52,400
I came here specially today

200
00:08:52,400 --> 00:08:53,320
to donate more merit money

201
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,440
to thank this Sorceress

202
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:55,440
for saving her life.

203
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:56,720
Is it really that magical?

204
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,080
Then

205
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,080
let's go get one too.

206
00:08:59,560 --> 00:09:00,080
This business with the Huang Family

207
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:00,960
is just too bizarre.

208
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,520
Exactly.

209
00:09:01,760 --> 00:09:02,320
Maybe we

210
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,760
are being dragged down by them.

211
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,520
We must get an amulet to stay safe.

212
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,640
Let's go, let's go!

213
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,440
Thank you, thank you.

214
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:09,720
Here's mine.

215
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,440
Inspector,

216
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,960
we just received news.

217
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:19,760
Several military strongholds

218
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,720
outside our city

219
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:21,960
have already been secretly monitored

220
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,320
by other warlords.

221
00:09:25,720 --> 00:09:27,080
They can't wait already.

222
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:28,640
Chun Cheng,

223
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,080
go tell the brothers

224
00:09:30,560 --> 00:09:31,440
to tighten security

225
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,840
and be ready for emergencies.

226
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:35,960
Let's see

227
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,440
what kind of tricks they can pull.

228
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,240
Yes, sir.

229
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,840
Have you heard?

230
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,920
The Huang Family angered heaven.

231
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:07,600
These successive disasters

232
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,560
are all retribution.

233
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,440
Isn't that the truth?

234
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,240
Even Master You Tong said so.

235
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,720
It seems Jiangyu City

236
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,240
is going to change hands soon.

237
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,560
More than just changing hands.

238
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,440
The Huang Family is a menace.

239
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,720
Right now, outside the city,

240
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,800
there are soldiers guarding everywhere.

241
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:20,920
Who knows, one day they might

242
00:10:20,920 --> 00:10:21,840
swarm in and slaughter us.

243
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:22,360
When that happens,

244
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,320
we'll be the ones to suffer.

245
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,080
That's right.

246
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,840
What should we do then?

247
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:26,080
If you ask me,

248
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,160
all these disasters

249
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,160
were caused by Huang Zhenyue.

250
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:29,840
Rather than waiting to become

251
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,720
meat on their chopping block,

252
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:31,720
we should go together

253
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,200
and make the Huang Family

254
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,480
get out of Jiangyu City!

255
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,200
Yeah!

256
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:34,800
Let's go!

257
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,480
Let's go!

258
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,200
Let's go!

259
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:37,200
Let's go!

260
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,800
Get out!

261
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,840
Get out of Jiangyu City!

262
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,840
Get out of Jiangyu City!

263
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,080
Get out of Jiangyu City!

264
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:44,440
Get out of Jiangyu City!
